Package test.java

Class IntegrationTest

java.lang.Object
test.java.IntegrationTest
class IntegrationTest extends Object
This class tests the application as a whole. For testing purposes
a robot is created, that simulates user inputs in different scenarios.
A full integration test takes approximately 70 seconds. Do not move
the mouse or press any keys while the test is running.
Author:
kevin
